# Directors Dealings — environment variable template.
#
# To activate:
#   1. Copy this file to `.env` in the project root.
#   2. Paste your real Anthropic API key after the `=` (no quotes, no spaces).
#   3. `.env` is gitignored. NEVER commit it.
#
# The Anthropic API key is your own — separate account, separate billing
# from Claude Code / Cowork. Get one from https://console.anthropic.com.
# Used by `.scripts/llm_parser.py` only when the regex parser flags a
# filing. The orchestrators honour --no-llm and --llm-budget-usd flags
# to keep spend bounded.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
